Careers at Sydney
Be part of something bigger
HeroChildModel(linkUtils=au.edu.sydney.commons.core.utils.LinkUtils@40fcacbd, ctaUrl=https://usyd.wd105.myworkdayjobs.com/USYD_EXTERNAL_CAREER_SITE, ctaDescription=Search our job database, arialabel=)
Join our supportive and inclusive community working to transform lives through the extraordinary power of world-class research and teaching.
We are proud to be recognised as an inclusive employer.
+61 2 8627 1200
recruitment@sydney.edu.au
[CARD]
Academic careers
        
An academic career at the University gives you the opportunity to collaborate in an intellectually dynamic environment. Join the best researchers in the world.
[CARD]
Professional careers
        
The University offers incredible professional career opportunities in diverse roles. See how you can work with brilliant minds, push boundaries and make a difference.
[CARD]
Careers for people with disability
        
The University of Sydney aspires to be an employer of choice for people with disability. Find out more about why you should work with us.
